data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of the Eastside! This affordable 1-story gem offers everything you need for comfortable living. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, it's perfect for all walks of life. Inside, you will find a bright and open floor plan, making every corner of this home feel inviting. Recent updates include new tile flooring and remodeled bathrooms, adding a fresh touch to your daily life. The 2-car garage provides ample storage space and protection for your vehicles. With a price tag of just $229,950, this home is a fantastic opportunity you won't want to miss. Contact us today for a tour or your broker! Side note, with our preferred lender, the sellers are also willing to cover the title policy!
